name: Experiment Or Die #49
description: Project to create a new collage every day for a year using my years of personal assets. For almost a week now I've been using the previous days layout as the base for the new design and the last few days I believe are starting to bear fruit. The colors, shapes and patterns that have been emerging are fantastic and if I can keep this up for the full year it could be the greatest ride of my life! Twitter and IG: Nikejerk
